summary:
Multilingual professional in international business, project & account management. Experience across Europe, Africa & Latin America. Creative in identifying and developing business opportunities in challenging contexts. Native Dutch and fluent in English, French and Spanish. Lived and worked abroad in Spain and Uganda.

Fields of expertise: 
International Business Development | Export | Import | Loyalty Marketing | Sales | Account Management | Hospitality | Travel | mHealth | Agriculture | Coffee | Tea | Consumer goods | Sustainability  | International Trade | Consulting  | FMCG | Renewable Energy | Innovation | Mobile4Development | ICT | SaaS Solutions| Africa | Latin-America | Spanish | French
